  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You'll have a buffet breakfast with hot and cold options and if you choose to upgrade to half board, dinner is a delicious four courses with various options. To start you'll have a salad buffet and to finish a dessert buffet and a cheese trolley. The food here is typical Italian with lots of pasta and pizza!</p>
<p><strong>Mon Amour </strong>is the hotels' bar which is also open to the public. This is a great place to enjoy your aperitivo at the end of the day.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
